{"tid":2131861,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"李家超：不排除立法監管傳媒 會搜證打擊宣揚「港獨」媒體","createTime":"2020-07-30T06:15:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T11:26:32.000Z","uid":240362,"like":32,"dislike":286,"uniUserReply":103,"replies":[{"pid":"805f973dc84e0beda9c499394a25b4e0e42163a6","tid":2131861,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:15:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200730/YYY64RMEABRKVNOBZS5E3BNBEE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200730%2FYYY64RMEABRKVNOBZS5E3BNBEE%2F&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhFUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=43482dd3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200730%2FYYY64RMEABRKVNOBZS5E3BNBEE%2F&h=9c4862b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200730/YYY64RMEABRKVNOBZS5E3BNBEE/</a><br />\n<br />\n「港版國安法」條文涵蓋的範圍廣泛，其中規管媒體方面，港府可採取「必要措施」，包括加強指導、監督和管理。保安局局長李家超接受《大公報》專訪時稱，將參考外國對媒體的管理制度及懲治方法，在保障新聞自由時，不排除立法監管傳媒，明言「有啲公開宣揚『港獨』嘅媒體，我哋會搜集證據打擊」。"},{"pid":"ecc845910294d49f6aa94b7044c369f9d56f3313","tid":2131861,"uid":82938,"like":142,"dislike":2,"score":140,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:16:57.000Z","msg":"駛乜立丫<br />\n你話有罪咪有罪囉"},{"pid":"c917d2d4e817716206d6ee42b8fb654c15a00fc2","tid":2131861,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ecc845910294d49f6aa94b7044c369f9d56f3313","tid":2131861,"uid":82938,"like":142,"dislike":2,"score":140,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:16:57.000Z","msg":"駛乜立丫<br />\n你話有罪咪有罪囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:17:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbc9d4f202dc55fbed77be3c52ed0db99ae920a0","tid":2131861,"uid":323319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":